FBI is offering a $20,000 reward for information about Bhadreshkumar Chetanbhai Patel's whereabouts . 
 He allegedly killed his wife, Palak Bhadreskumar Patel, on April 12 in Hanover, Maryland . 
 Taxi driver told investigators she drove him to a hotel in Newark, New Jersey . 
 Patel was last seen in surveillance footage at a Best Western near Newark Liberty International Airport on April 13 . 
 Police believe that he is still in the U.S. and is considered to be dangerous . 
 